rows.label: qst640406_msg0002
rows.name:
Ah, right. Renata sent you as
reinforcements, eh? That's my girl!

rows.label: qst640406_msg0003
rows.name:
You couldn't have come at
a better time, either.

rows.label: qst640406_msg0004
rows.name:
You probably know by now
that this plant is in need
of some tender loving care.

rows.label: qst640406_msg0005
rows.name:
Amir's dispatched me to
deal with the repairs on
the second floor, but...

rows.label: qst640406_msg0006
rows.name:
Some swarming insects have made
a nest right in front of the
critical malfunctioning part.

rows.label: qst640406_msg0007
rows.name:
If you could just take care
of those, I should be able to
get in and work my magic...

rows.label: qst640406_msg0008
rows.name:
Man, you're nice to have around...
Though I shouldn't expect any less
from Drivers chosen by my girl!

rows.label: qst640406_msg0009
rows.name:
Right, so! Defeat those buzzing
bastards and wreck their nest,
and then we'll be golden.

rows.label: qst640406_msg0101
rows.name:
Defeat those buzzing bastards and
wreck their nest for me, please.

rows.label: qst640406_msg0102
rows.name:
That way I'll be able to
get to the part that's
broken and work my magic.

rows.label: qst640406_msg0201
rows.name: Well, the insects certainly seem gone.

rows.label: qst640406_msg0202
rows.name:
Thank you for that. Now I
can finally get to work.

rows.label: qst640406_msg0203
rows.name:
Renata... Just wait a tiny bit
longer, baby. I'll be home soon!

rows.label: qst640406_msg0204
rows.name:
Papa's gettin' to work,
and when Papa gets to
work, the work gets DONE!
